data.description: Come see this beautiful 5 bedroom 3baths, 2 car garage, home in the Sendera Ranch community. The home features an open concept with a fireplace in the living room. The kitchen features include a large granite island and plenty of storage. There is tile flooring throughout to make for easy cleaning with carpet in the bedrooms. Out back enjoy the extended covered patio and large yard. This community offers more amenities than one can count!
